==English==

===Alternative spellings===
* Labour is the only accepted spelling in [[Wikipedia:Commonwealth English|Commonwealth English]].
* [[labor|Labor]] is the only spelling recognised as correct in [[Wikipedia:American English|American English]].
* There are special cases in [[Wikipedia:Australian English|Australian English]] where the US ''labor'' spelling is used, eg the [[Wikipedia:Australian Labor Party|Australian Labor Party]].

